title: The Artie Quitter Podcast SEP 21 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Geno Bisconte, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.




TODAY's SHOW  (02:23:04)


Artie, Chris Cotton & Geno Bisconte are Joined by columnist & film critic RICHARD ROEPER. Later Stuttering JOHN MELENDEZ
